videos.description: Jalen Brunson dishes to Omari Spellman who knocks down a 3-pointer as the shot clock winds down.
videos.headline: Villanova's Spellman drills three before buzzer

videos.description: Marcus Foster blows by Mikal Bridges and lays in a bucket for Creighton.
videos.headline: Creighton's Foster goes baseline for layup

videos.description: Jacob Epperson attempts a layup but Donte DiVincenzo comes flying in for the shot block.
videos.headline: Villanova's DiVincenzo denies Epperson at the rim

videos.description: Villanova's Donte DiVincenzo jumps the pass and beats two Creighton defenders down the court for a layup.
videos.headline: DiVincenzo steals and scores

videos.description: Jalen Brunson drains a corner 3-pointer and draws a foul for a chance at a 4-point play.
videos.headline: Villanova's Brunson earns 4-point play

videos.description: Mikal Bridges drives to the lane and uses his length to make a layup while drawing a foul.
videos.headline: Villanova's Bridges makes acrobatic layup

videos.description: Marcus Foster steals the ball and races up the court for a fast-break layup.
videos.headline: Foster's defense leads to easy bucket for Creighton
